text: Camille Simoine Winbush (born February 9, 1990) is an American actor, voice talent and comedian. She was born in Culver City, California. She is perhaps best known for acting in The Bernie Mac Show. == References == == Other websites == * Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:American voice actors Category:Comedians from Los Angeles County, California Category:Actors from Culver City, California
